          "reviewBody": "Cambridge International school is one great place for big events, both indoor and outdoor. They have lush green fields, a great spacious auditorium and a fantastic cafe cum canteen. Sports and Cultural events here will be a great one as there is a lot of space to host a lot of people like 500-600 at a time. The school part is a premium one as it's one of the most premium schools of Kolkata.\nThe place is great for events, auditions and outdoor activities.",
