          "reviewBody": "No extra stress on anything. Academics is dealt with in a very simple but effective way. They pay attention to the students dreams and what they want to do. I am happy to recommend TCIS as it is one of the Best International Schools in Kolkata  Balance between extra-curricular activities and academics is perfect.",
